blog.description: Everything before the word 'but' is horse shit. - Jon Snow

body:
THE MOUNTAIN & THE VIPER

LF: First time I saw you, you were just a child. A girl from the North come to the capital for the first time. You’re not a child any longer. Why did you help me?

Sansa: They would have thrown you through the Moon Door if they found you guilty.

LF: That’s not an answer.

Sansa: If they’d have executed you, what would they have done with me?

LF: I don’t know.

Sansa: Neither do I.

LF: Better to gamble on the man you know than the strangers you don’t? And you think you know me?

Sansa: I know what you want.

LF: Do you?

Better to gamble on the man you know than the strangers you don’t? And you think you know me?

blog.name: dragon-of-the-soutn
blog.title: TheWritingStudio
blog.description: Hey! A pansexual girl who is in to many fandoms to be healthy! But this blog only really posts about Game of thrones, Star Wars the clone wars and now apparently The dragon prince!

body:
Opinion time

Me: takes a deep breath.

I don’t ship Jon x Daenerys.

Hundreds of swords all point at me at once. Before you turn my blog into the red wedding hear me out.

It’s not because I don’t like the characters. For all her flaws Dany has been one of my favourite characters since the beginning and Jon is Jon. He’s hard not to like.

It’s not because of the incest. I can understand it’s a different time and I can get over that.

It’s not because I ship other opposing ships that there in. I’m pretty neutral to that and have no intention of getting mixed up in a shipping war!

If they were just great friends I would of loved that! I literally squealed when Jon and Dany first got a scene together!

I just can’t get behind it. And I’ve tried ok! I’ve read the fanfics, I’ve looked at the fan art (some of it is amazing by the way!) I just can’t do it. And I’m not hear to hate on people who ship it. If Jon and Dany float your boat then keep doing what your doing and love that ship.

I think I’ll just stick to captaining the SS Braime (Jamie x Brienne) and continue to live in denial about Throbb (Theon x Robb) and Margaery x Sansa living happily ever after.

This is the Dragon of the soutn sighing off. Have a great day everyone!
